                            <comment id="412006" author="sebastien" created="Mon, 22 Apr 2024 07:07:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Not really. The issue reported by Coverity cannot happen thanks to the checks on the buffers, carried out before the call to strcpy(). But it is always better to clean up code, which is why patch #54710 was pushed.&lt;/p&gt;

